Story: Oauth
	As an user
	I want to access the site from a client application
	So that I can create/access/update/delete/start workflows, definitions
	
	Scenario: Authorized User CRUDs definitions
		Given an authorized user named: 'alice' and password: 'alice'
		When user registers client 'test'	
		And user grants access to client 'test' realm '/wfcs/'	
		Then the user can create a new definition
		And the user can publish the definition
		And the user can get the definition
		And the user can delete the definition